data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bed, 2 bath gem with original hardwood floors! You will love the open floor plan offering a large living room, formal dining room perfect for family gatherings. The eat-in kitchen is large with updated cabinetry (in progress). You'll love the enclosed sun porch, which can be utilized as an office or cozy retreat. Conveniently located on the main floor, the laundry room adds an extra level of convenience to your daily routine. The master bedroom has an ensuite bath, perfect for privacy. 2 additional bedrooms and a hall bath complete the main floor. The full finished walkout basement offers endless possibilities.  An additional room in the basement adds flexibility making this home a 4 bedroom haven for a growing family or those in need of extra space. Step outside and be amazed by the expansive backyard, providing ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation.
